the chinese government 's stand on the taiwan issue is consistent , that is , to adhere to the basic principle of " peaceful reunification and one country , two systems . "
therefore , we have made every effort to show the greatest sincerity and done a lot of work .
however , our efforts have been provocative from the taiwan authorities and the " taiwan independence " forces .
we respect the democratic demands of the taiwan people , but we oppose the taiwan authorities and the " taiwan independence " forces in the name of democracy to engage in " taiwan independence " activities and separate taiwan from the motherland .
the reason why we clearly show our determination and will to safeguard the reunification of the motherland is to safeguard peace and stability in the taiwan strait region .
we have stated that as long as there is a line of hope , we will do our best to realize the reunification of the motherland through peaceful means .
we appreciate president bush 's repeated adherence to the one - china stance and have issued a clear signal to the " taiwan independence " forces .
the leader of the taiwan authorities claimed that " in order to prevent china from using force to infringe on taiwan , one - sided change of the status quo between the two sides of the strait , it is necessary to promote a peace referendum . "
this is a slander of the mainland 's peace efforts , and is also a provocation to cross - strait relations .
at present , the actual threat to taiwan 's security is not from the mainland , but from the taiwan authorities ' wanton activities of " taiwan independence . "
the " taiwan independence " separatist force is the direct source of undermining the status quo of cross - strait relations and jeopardizing peace in the taiwan strait .
the taiwan authorities have distorted the mainland 's opposition to " taiwan independence " splitting and safeguarding stability in the taiwan strait as an excuse to suppress taiwan 's democracy and freedom and use this as an excuse to launch a referendum .
this is groundless and confused right and wrong , and is meant to win sympathy and support for the continued implementation of the separatist line .
the leader of the taiwan authorities claimed that he would hold a so - called " defensive referendum " and " a peace referendum , " but such provocative behavior will only trigger confrontation and hostility between the two sides of the strait , aggravate cross - strait tension , and push cross - strait relations to the brink of danger step by step .
this completely runs counter to the mainstream public opinion of the taiwan compatriots for peace , stability , and development , and is not the deepening of taiwan 's " democracy , " but is also a serious threat to the taiwan people and a serious threat to peace and stability in the asia - pacific region , and is bound to be universally opposed by the compatriots on both sides of the strait and the international community .
taking a general look at the historical process of the development of the chinese nation , reunification is always the main current , and is the trend of the times and the will of the people .
with the growing strength of the motherland and the constant strengthening of cross - strait cooperation , the international community has generally recognized the one - china pattern , and any separatist conspiracy is doomed to failure .
