since the birth of the intellectual property system several hundred years ago , especially since the industrial revolution , it has hastened the birth of another major invention of epoch - making significance .
over the past 20 years , the intellectual property system has become the basic legal system and important policy means of various countries in promoting technological innovation , and has played an important role in rejuvenating the economy and enhancing international competitiveness .
with the rapid development of science and technology and economic globalization , the creation , occupation , and application of intellectual and intellectual resources , and the number and quality of intellectual property rights , have become an important foundation for all countries to participate in international competition .
therefore , international exchanges and cooperation to strengthen the protection of intellectual property rights are of great significance to establishing a just and rational new international economic order and promoting economic prosperity and development in the world .
the chinese government attaches great importance to the protection of intellectual property rights .
in the early days of reform and opening up , china began to establish a intellectual property system , and through more than 20 years of efforts , it has established a relatively complete system of intellectual property rights ( ipr ) , and has established a system of ipr protection with administrative law enforcement , and has done a great deal of work in protecting intellectual property rights , thus making important contributions to promoting scientific and technological progress and economic and social development .
as mankind entered the information society in the 21 st century , the scientific and technological revolution will promote the development of the social productive forces with an unprecedented huge driving force .
further improving china 's intellectual property system and strengthening international exchanges and cooperation in the protection of intellectual property rights is a requirement for china to open up wider to the outside world in the new century , and is also a need for building a socialist modern country and realizing the great rejuvenation of the chinese nation .
we are willing to work together with all countries in the world to establish a fair and reasonable intellectual property system that is conducive to promoting the development of science and technology and economy , and to creating a good environment for the whole of mankind to respect intellectual property rights , advocate science , and protect intellectual property rights .
