the us government announced on 18 november that it has decided to impose quotas on the three categories of textile products , namely , the needle of the chinese imports .
when china continues to make efforts to expand economic and trade cooperation between china and the united states , the us government 's trade protectionism measure cannot but cause people to regret .
as of today , economic globalization has developed to a new level of restrictions on china 's textile imports , it is extremely inappropriate for the united states to impose quotas on china .
first of all , such a move of abusing the " quota " has restricted the implementation of the principle of free trade of the world trade organization .
on the one hand , he talked about " free trade , " and on the other hand , he has often let it be known that the " quota " cold arrow can be used to build trade barriers , and this is not a matter of the overhauls and the loss of public agreement .
second , " quota " has restricted the good development momentum of sino - us economic and trade relations .
since china and the united states reached an agreement on china 's accession to the wto in 1999 , us exports to china have grown by an average annual rate of 15 percent .
from january to september this year , us exports to china increased by 26.2 percent over the same period last year .
in the past two years , the united states ' export of raw materials and manufactured goods to china has increased by a big margin .
in fact , today 's china has become the fastest growing country in the world in terms of exports to other countries .
