last year , it was the " year of culture and education " set by the international olympic committee .
taking advantage of this favorable opportunity , the beijing organizing committee has held a series of educational activities to disseminate advanced culture and popularize olympic knowledge .
among them , the " study of olympic knowledge for secondary school students " , which mainly consists of young people , is a very important achievement .
this reader , which is also a fictitious and vivid introduction of the knowledge and olympic spirit of the olympic movement , is a good teaching material that will help young students enhance their understanding of the olympic movement and help them improve their enthusiasm for participating in the olympic games .
last year , the beijing organizing committee also specially designed the models for young students to produce renewable paper and bear the beijing olympic games logo .
the concept of " green olympic games " is to prepare for and host the olympic games with a view to protecting the environment and protecting the ecological balance .
we hope that these models can act like the regulations , standardize the conduct of young students , and make them gradually become the practice promoters and promoters of the " green olympic " concept .
education is one of the core contents of the olympic movement , and is also an important embodiment of the " humanities olympic games . "
the true purpose of the olympic movement is to educate young people from a new angle and in a new way , promote the healthy and healthy development of young people , and make contributions to the establishment of a peaceful and beautiful world .
therefore , the combination of sports and education has not only opened up new worlds for the development of education , but also made the olympic movement more of educational significance .
the " green olympic games " are one of the three major ideas for beijing to host the 2008 olympic games .
the core content is to greatly improve the environmental quality of the capital , create a beautiful environment and build an ecological city for the olympic games .
to this end , it is necessary to extensively adopt environmental protection technology and means , promote environmental control , urban and rural greening , and develop environmental protection industries , and constantly enhance the awareness of the whole society on environmental protection and encourage the public to actively participate in various activities to improve the ecological environment .
doing a good job in implementing the " green olympic games " is an important task for us to adhere to the principle of taking people as the foundation , establish a comprehensive , coordinated , and sustainable scientific concept of development , and promote comprehensive , coordinated , and sustainable economic and social development in beijing .
we must attach great importance to this .
in order to achieve the goals of the green olympic games , beijing has formulated the " olympic action plan " and the " plan for ecological and environmental protection " on the basis of the " 10th five - year plan " and the " plan for the protection of the environment , " and has formulated new objectives and plans for environmental construction and protection in the next few years .
it will comprehensively realize the goal of holding a green olympic games through a planned and systematic implementation .
