( international ) us flu virus spreading peak
xinhua news agency report of december 31 from los angeles ( by staff reporter yan liang ) - the us centers for disease control and prevention said on the 31 st that the united states has reached a peak for more than 30 years , with 45 of the 50 states in the united states , the number of cases of influenza in the region has increased rapidly .
according to statistics released by the center on december 20 , the number of deaths caused by influenza in the united states has reached a record of 7.8% of all deaths in the same period .
at least 42 children died of influenza in the united states , and the number of adult deaths has also increased rapidly , but at present it is still not yet accurate .
experts believe that there are two reasons for the serious spread of influenza in 2003 : first , the influenza virus is not a " panama - type " virus , which is not a popular flu virus in previous years . second , the united states has been unable to effectively prevent the flu virus , and the two major suppliers have reduced the output to 83 million vaccines this year .
although about 60,000 people died of influenza every year in the united states , 1.14 million people were admitted in hospital for influenza , such as the flu has led to a certain degree of social panic .
the us epidemiologist williams said that this flu was the most serious in the past 30 years , and that the flu was even greater than in previous years , and the flu was spread in many schools , and many of the places where the flu vaccines were vaccinated .
in the face of such a grim situation , the us health department launched an emergency handling center on 19 december and sent medical experts teams to various states .
three killed in traffic accident in zhejiang
xinhua news agency , hangzhou , january 1 , an extraordinarily serious traffic accident occurred in the early morning of the 1 st in the ningbo county of zhejiang province .
as a result , three people in the car were killed and four injured in a car accident , which was full of dense fog in the air .
at about 2 : 00 am on the 1 st , the driver was driving a red - colored taxi , which was a red flag , from linhai to ningbo , and carrying six passengers on the vehicle .
at that time , it was very foggy , and the view was not clear .
when the two - way passageway were travelling to the two - way passageway , the taxi and a large lorry collided with a total of 3,378 km of the same direction .
it was learned that at that time , the large goods vehicle entered the main lane of the lane , but the taxi was not allowed to avoid the collision , and the vehicle was seriously deformed , and three of the seven people , including the driver , were killed .
after the accident occurred , the traffic police department of zhejiang province promptly issued a circular urging the traffic police department of the whole province to take immediate measures to strengthen traffic management under bad weather conditions , prevent vehicle overload and speeding up the accident , and ensure the safety of road traffic during the spring festival .
