xinhua news agency , tehran , january 1 , iranian national radio said on the 1 st that the iranian search and rescue workers on the 31 st and the 1 st found 14 survivors .
the staff of the iranian red crescent society rescued a young shop owner from the counter on the 1 st , said : " we have saved at least one life .
i 've been to the battlefield and experienced many tests , but i have never been so happy . "
iranian national radio said the search and rescue workers also rescued a nine - year - old girl and a pregnant woman from the housing ruins on the same day .
their physical condition is very weak .
a total of 11 survivors , including a four - month - old baby and a 80 - year - old woman , were found on the 31 st .
however , rescue personnel believe that with the passage of time , the chances of the survivors are very slim .
according to statistics , about 280,000 dead bodies have been found at the site of the earthquake and some of the dead bodies have been buried .
in addition , they rescued 2,000 survivors from the ruins of the ruins , and most of them were discovered the following day after the earthquake occurred .
according to the latest information from the earthquake - hit areas and other channels , the number of people killed in the quake is expected to increase to 340,000 , the un humanitarian coordination office said today .
