( international ) israeli deputy prime minister denies plans to expand settlement in golan heights
xinhua news agency , london , january 2 , israeli deputy prime minister olmert denied on the 2 nd that israel plans to expand jewish settlements in the golan heights , claiming that there is no such " plan " or such " policy . "
the israeli government plans to increase the number of jewish settlers living in the golan heights before the peace talks with syria on december 31 last year to strengthen control over the golan heights , israeli minister of agriculture said in a statement .
in an interview with the british broadcasting corporation , olmert said that the development of agriculture , tourism , and settlements in the golan heights was wrong .
he said : " in the past two days , i have repeatedly verified the premier and the finance minister . in accordance with the government 's commitments , i have not been approved . "
he said that despite some ministers ' consent to this plan , the government will never give any support .
the golan heights was captured by israel in the third middle east war in 1967 with a total of 1.70,000 jewish settlers .
syria and israel are therefore in a state of war for a long time .
after the publication of the golan heights 's remarks immediately aroused widespread concern in the international community , syria condemned israel 's plan to expand the golan heights , stressing that this was illegal .
china 's high - tech modern weapons industry has now become " embryonic "
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 3 ( reporter li huanyan and li bin ) in the past year , the china ordnance industry corporation , as one of the top 10 military industrial enterprises in china , has made great progress in the research and development of high - tech weapons and equipment and in reform and extrication from difficulties .
