at the same time , the china ordnance industry corporation has made great efforts to promote structural adjustment , and the total number of employees has been reduced to 360,000 , and the total number of employees has been reduced from 47.60,000 to 360,000 , and the net staff and workers have been reorganized and listed on the stock market .
( international ) mongolia 's livestock industry improved in 2003
xinhua news agency , ulan bator , january 5 ( reporter lu guodong ) according to local media reports on the 5 th , by the end of 2003 , the volume of the livestock keeping in mongolia was 2530.78 million , an increase of 162.33 million over the same period last year .
this was the first time since the sharp decline in the livestock reserves in mongolia .
with a huge rain in summer last year , spring and winter have not met with heavy snow , creating favorable conditions for the improvement of the situation in mongolia 's livestock industry .
by the end of 2003 , there were a total of 255.56 million camels of the camilla , 195.83 million , 178.43 million cattle , and 100.62 million sheep , and the mountain sheep was 100.34 million .
compared with the same period last year , there was an increase in the number of camel camel , mountain sheep , and mianyang , while the number of buffalos was somewhat reduced .
mongolia 's livestock and poultry industries basically privatized in the 1990 s .
however , the livestock and poultry industries after privatization are completely " dependent on heaven . "
from 1994 to 1999 , the mongolian animal husbandry industry had been thriving for six years in a row , due to inclement weather .
at the end of 1999 , mongolia 's livestock reserves reached 3.35 million , a record high .
however , from 2000 to 2002 , the province 's livestock industry experienced three consecutive years of heavy snow and drought in the winter .
at the end of 2002 , mongolia 's livestock keeping number was only 22.645 million , down 91.55 million in three years .
( international ) north korea says it will use military force against the united states
xinhua news agency , pyongyang , january 6 , the dprk central news agency issued a commentary on the 6 th , urging the united states to make good efforts to resolve the nuclear issue , and said that the dprk will vigorously strengthen its military strength and use military force against the united states .
the commentary said : the most important thing in easing the tense situation on the korean peninsula and safeguarding peace and stability on the korean peninsula is to settle the nuclear issue between the dprk and the united states peacefully through dialogue .
the dprk has put forward a package of solution to the issue on the basis of the principle of simultaneously taking action as the basis .
the commentary reiterated that the peaceful settlement of the nuclear issue through dialogue is a consistent principled stand of the dprk .
the us government should adopt a goodwill toward this stance of the dprk .
however , the united states is going to test its weapons and other advanced weapons on the afghan and iraqi battlefield in the near future , and is speeding up its preparations for starting a new war .
the commentary also said that the dprk will adopt a self - defense policy that " the united states is totally denying and threatening the dprk 's ideology and system , and that the dprk will take the initiative to deal with the issue with the dprk , which is a matter of the dprk 's defense of sovereignty and the right to survival , and the peace and stability of the korean peninsula and the region . "
the greater the us threat , the more the dprk will further strengthen its anti - imperialist military front and use its military strength to cope with the united states .
( international ) us service industry continues to grow behind manufacturing
xinhua news agency , new york , january 6 , ( reporter xue yanping ) a report released by the well - known us research institute on the 6 th showed that the index of the service industry in the united states dropped in january last year , indicating that the current growth of the service industry is still behind the manufacturing industry .
the report said that in january last year , the index of service industries , including retail , financial , construction , and other non - manufacturing sectors , decreased from 60.1 percent in the previous month to 58.6 percent , and the economists estimated that the index would increase to 60.5 percent .
according to the standards set by the supply management association , the service industry index is higher than the 50 - sector expansion , while the service industry represents less than 50 percent of the industry .
the index of manufacturing industries grew by a big margin in the second half of the year , the highest in 20 years , according to a report released today by the supply management association .
this shows that the growth of the us service industry is still behind the manufacturing sector .
the growth of the manufacturing sector is conducive to expanding employment and promoting economic growth , but the growth of the service sector will play a greater role in reducing unemployment and promoting economic growth .
